headlines.description: Ante Rebic broke his AC Milan duck by scoring two second-half goals including a stoppage-time winner to give them a thrilling 3-2 win over Udinese.
headlines.shortLinkText: Milan snatch stoppage time win over Udinese

venue.fullName: Stadio Ettore Giardiniero - Via del Mare

headlines.description: Inter Milan were held to a 1-1 draw by relegation-battling Lecce in Serie A on Sunday, dropping points for the second weekend in a row.
headlines.shortLinkText: Inter draw at Lecce as title hopes take big hit

venue.displayName: Stadio Ettore Giardiniero - Via del Mare

headlines.description: AS Roma returned to winning ways and moved into fourth place in Serie A with a 3-1 win at troubled Genoa on Sunday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Roma go fourth with win that deepens Genoa crisis

headlines.description: Cristiano Ronaldo struck twice to continue his sensational scoring run and help move Juventus four points clear at the top of Serie A.
headlines.shortLinkText: Ronaldo double fires Juve four points clear
